HEADWORD: Postnate
<hw>Post"nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>postnatus</ets> second or subsequently born; L. <ets>post</ets>
after + <ets>natus</ets> born.]</ety> <def>Subsequent.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The
graces and gifts of the spirit are <xex>postnate</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<mark>[Archaic]</mark> <rj><au>Jer. Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
